snippet: Heart, a 3-year-old Labrador retriever, won the Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show’s obedience competition with a display of deportment that included fetching a few heart-print pillows.
abstract: Labrador retriever named Heart wins obedience competition at Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show.
